obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line 3
  line `THE BANNING OF UNREGULATED DEPOSIT SCHEMES ACT, 2019`
  line `ACT NO. 21 OF 2019`
  line `[ 3 1 st July, 2019.]`
  line `An Act to provide for a comprehensive mechanism to ban the unregulated deposit schemes, other than`
  line `deposits taken in the ordinary course of business, and to protect the interest of depositors and for`
  line `matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
  line `BE it enacted by Parliament in the Seventieth Year of the Republic of India as follows: —`
  line `CHAPTER I`
  line `P RELIMINARY`
  line `1. Short title, extent and commencement. — ( 1 ) This Act may be called the Banning of Unregulated`
  line `Deposit Schemes Act, 2019.`
  line `( 2 ) It extends to the who le of India * except the State of Jammu and Kashmir.`
  line `( 3 ) It shall be deemed to have come into force on the 21st day of February, 2019`
  line `2. Definitions — In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires, —`
  line `( 1 ) “appropriate Government” means in respect of matters relating to, —`
  line `( i ) the Union territory without legislature, the Central Government;`
  line `( ii ) the Union territory of Puducherry, the Government of that Union territory;`
  line `( iii ) the Union territory of Delhi, the Governmen t of that Union territory; and;`
  line `( iv ) the State, the State Government;`
  line `( 2 ) “company” shall have the same meaning as assigned to it in clause (20) of section 2 of the`
  line `Companies Act, 2013 (18 of 2013);`
  line `( 3 ) “Competent Authority” means an Authority appointed by the appropriate Government under section 7;`
  line `( 4 ) “deposit” means an amount of money received by way of an advance or loan or in any other form, by any`
  line `deposit taker with a promise to return whether after a specified period or otherwise, either in cash o r in kind or in the`
  line `form of a specified service, with or without any benefit in the form of interest, bonus, profit or in any other form, but`
  line `does not include —`
  line `( a ) amounts received as loan from a scheduled bank or a co - operative bank or any other banking company as`
  line `defined in section 5 of the Banking Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of 1949);`
  line `( b ) amounts received as loan or financial assistance from the Public Financial Institutions notified by the`
  line `Central Government in consultation with the Reserve Bank of India or any non - banking financial company as`
  line `defined in clause ( f ) of section 45 - I of the Reserve Bank of India Act, 1934 (2 of 1934) and is registered with the`
  line `Reserve Bank of India or any Regional Financial Institutions or insurance companies;`
  line `*. Now applica ble to the Union territory of Jammu and Kashmir and the Union territory of Ladakh by vide notification No. S.O.`
  line `3912 (E), dated 30th October, 2019.`
  line .
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  kind page
  sectionId pdf-page-4
  sectionNo (4)
