  line `45 - I of the Reserve Bank of India`
  line `Act, 1934 (2 of 1934) and`
  line `registered with the Reserve Bank`
  line `of India; or any other scheme or an`
  line `arrangement registered under the`
  line `Reserve Bank of India Act, 1934.`
