  line `under which funds are accepted by`
  line `individual s or entities engaged as`
  line `Business Correspondents and`
  line `Facilitators by banks subject to the`
  line `guidelines and circulars issued by`
  line `the Reserve Bank of India from`
  line `time to time.`
  line `(iii) Any scheme or an arrangement`
  line `under which funds are received by`
  line `a system provider operating as an`
