  line `9. The Ministr y of Corporate Affairs,`
  line `Government of India`
  line `(i) Deposits accepted or permitted`
  line `under the provisions of Chapter V`
  line `of the Companies Act, 2013 (18 of`
  line `2013).`
  line `(ii) Any scheme or an arrangement`
  line `under which deposits are accepted`
  line `by a company declared as a Nidh i`
  line `or a Mutual Benefit Society under`
  line `section 406 of the Companies Act,`
  line `2013 (18 of 2013).`
  line `( 2 ) The following shall also be treated as Regulated Deposit Schemes under this Act, namely: —`
  line `( a ) deposits accepted under any scheme or an arrangement registered with any regulatory body in India`
  line `constituted or established under a statute; and`
  line `( b ) any other scheme as may be notified by the Central Government under this Act.`
